Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能在催眠师给我戴上勋章之后才变得毫无畏惧\N{\fnArial\fs38}I was only fearless because a hypnotist put a medallion around my neck.
