Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要死了啦\N{\fnArial\fs38}I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\fnArial\fs38}Ah, bad idea!
